Od tvog dragog brata?

322
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:31,750
Ima i za njega jedna.

323
00:35:31,880 --> 00:35:34,030
To ga opravdava?

324
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:37,356
Ceka na mene.

325
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:39,436
Ne ceka.

326
